Nyeri members of county assembly were the highest paid in the Mt Kenya region within the first three months of the 2020/2021 financial year.
This is according to the latest report by the controller of budget report, which indicates that each of the ward representatives received an average of Sh119,600 monthly, up from Sh107,887 in the same period in the last financial year.



